  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"GUROBU\" </strong>is a story-driven, 2D horror game about haunted apartments, ghosts of the past, and a murder mystery.<br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1.5+ hour long.<br></li><li>5 endings!<br></li><li>5 nightmares to explore!<br></li><li>Name your cat!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTROLS:</h2><br>Arrows = Move<br><br>SPACE, Z or ENTER = Examine / Advance text<br><br>F4 / ALT+ENTER = Fullscreen<br><br>ESC, X = Menu / Cancel/Erase (text)",
